Gigan flying by the CF in his stasis pod when he notices the battle going on 
down on the ground. Eager for battle he lands and steps out of his stasis pod 
in his new dinosaur mode. 
"Gigan Maximize!" he yells with a roar from his beast mode.
Once in robot mode he gets his missile launcher and blast cannon ready. Then 
he runs over to the Maximal's side to help them out.
